   <li><a href="../../mobile/using/mobile-apps-ondemand.md">Authoring AEM Content for AEM Mobile On-Demand Services App</a></li> 
  </ul> 
  <note> 
   <p>To preview the app contents, including browse pages and articles, see <a href="../../mobile/using/aem-mobile-manage-ondemand-services.md">Previewing with Preflight</a>.</p> 
  </note> 
